verbose_text: These included replication fork associated proteins such as the single-strand DNA binding protein (SSB); the replicative helicase MCM; the MCM interacting factor Gins23; sliding clamp subunits PCNA1, 2, and 3; DNA ligase; replicative DNA polymerase polB1; and the clamp loader RFC.
